  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for freetype2",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for freetype2 fixes the following issues\n\n- Update to version 2.14.3\n- CVE-2026-23865: Integer overflow in the tt_var_load_item_variation_store function (bsc#1259118).\n- CVE-2026-50811: out-of-bounds read vulnerabilityin src/truetype/ttgxvar.c in the TT_Get_Var_Design implementation used by FT_Get_Var_Design_Coordinates (bsc#1271045).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
